data.description: Welcome home to this charming little bungalow. Beautifully Updated with modern finishes. Gorgeous engineered hardwood flooring. The living room features big bay windows that bring in all the natural sunlight. The kitchen features stainless-steel appliances and stylish cabinets with sleek countertops. Step outside through the kitchen door to the expansive fully-fenced backyard with large shed. Raised garden beds for the green thumb. Two car tandem parking and space for your travel trailer. Great location near American Lake, parks, shopping, restaurants, I-5, and more.
